Burning Hammer looks to see Trinity. He stares at Trinity, and all he can
think about is the annoying kid he wanted to kill. He turned his blaster at
Trinity. He aims dead on and his finger climbs onto the trigger...

----- Original Message -----
From: "Logo morph" <logomorph@...>
To: <nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com>
Sent: Friday, March 16, 2001 11:16 AM
Subject: Trinity


> ::Trinity::
>
> Being the kitten that she was, she decided to go out and play. After all,
a
> predacon sabertooth tiger kitten needs to stretch her legs once in a
while.
> She went outside and started running into the dense underbush.  She was
> growling a kitten growl and having fun.  She saw a small butterfly and
> decided to chase it.  She swatted at it and  growled, trying to be as
fierce
> as she could.  She ran about 4 miles before she stopped and looked around.
> She sat down and tried to get her barings. She hadn't payed attention to
how
> she got there in the first place, so she had no idea how she got there.
She
> called out a kitten roar and hoped someone might help her back to her
> friends.
